WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.780 --> 00:00:03.419
Girl 1: A museum to me is a place of expression.

00:00:03.640 --> 00:00:06.680
Boy: MoMA is one of those places where art
can mean pretty much anything.

00:00:06.860 --> 00:00:08.100
Girl 2: MoMA for me is a home.

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:09.960
Man 1: Where every idea is accepted.

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:12.140
Woman 1: You could be moved.

00:00:12.140 --> 00:00:13.140
You could be surprised.

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:15.960
Woman 2: Everybody should have a MoMA.

00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:17.320
It's nurturing.

00:00:17.320 --> 00:00:18.440
It's welcoming.

00:00:18.900 --> 00:00:22.540
Man 2: In 2019, MoMA will be explosive.

00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:29.180
Ana: The new performance space will be the
integral part of the collection galleries.

00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:34.720
Lana: We are constantly challenging ourselves.

00:00:35.800 --> 00:00:38.320
Woman 1: It's a living, breathing collection.

00:00:38.320 --> 00:00:41.560
We can remix it so that it's responding to
the world around us.

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:46.060
Glenn: Putting works of art in conversation
with each other in ways that have not happened

00:00:46.060 --> 00:00:47.160
before here.

00:00:47.560 --> 00:00:49.560
Paola: It's tremendously exciting.

00:00:49.560 --> 00:00:50.980
We're just at the beginning.

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:54.540
Glenn: In 2019, MoMA will be exhilarating.

00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:56.700
I'll just leave it at that.

